Hello! I'm a graduate student from George Washington University with a passion for backend engineering and system design. As a Software Engineer, I have designed APIs, maintained servers for an observability product, conducted code reviews, and created automated CI/CD pipelines. Eager to venture into freelancing, I am excited to apply my skills and knowledge to new and challenging projects in the backend engineering domain.
